{"tid":1167773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青山醫院多名醫生被點名恐嚇 警接手調查","createTime":"2019-05-23T09:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T09:12:25.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"34ee323769aca71d50114aeed7ac9797abe8045c","tid":1167773,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:12:25.000Z","msg":"早上9時52分，屯門青山醫院接獲三通恐嚇電話，接線職員大驚報警。警方將案件列作刑事恐嚇，由屯門警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n消息指出，今早青山醫院內一名41歲姓連社康護士接獲三通恐嚇電話，對方多次揚言放火燒毁醫院，並點名要姦殺數名法醫精神科部及成人精神科部的醫生。護士報案，院方及後向職員發出風險警告，通知各職員提高警覺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190523/s00001/1558597473543/%E9%9D%92%E5%B1%B1%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E9%BB%9E%E5%90%8D%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8E%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190523%2Fs00001%2F1558597473543%2F%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=06421104\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190523%2Fs00001%2F1558597473543%2F%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&h=6d940737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190523/s00001/1558597473543/%E9%9D%92%E5%B1%B1%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E9%BB%9E%E5%90%8D%E6%81%90